CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 9, 1963, pg. 4, reads: "To Tea - Pretty Yvonne Kemp modeled this tea time knit suit in green and white, part of the Italian knit Dupont collection featured at the D.I. affair of Sunday night. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Yvonne Jones Kemp wearing flecked skirt and suit jacket with matching hat, posing in the Holiday House for D.I.'s annual MENDS benefit
